      <trans-unit id="11022" identifier="01fea73dbf2916d568a3405ec150e02c">
        <source>The step by step process of counting the number of black squares in each row and identifying whether the parity is even, and then repeating the process with each column, is an example of an algorithm.</source>
        <target>crwdns11022:0crwdne11022:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[2]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="11023" identifier="9604303368ba30fed71114445270b0ca">
        <source>The full error detection algorithm includes what to to do when the error is found as well.</source>
        <target>crwdns11023:0crwdne11023:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[2]</note>
      </trans-unit>
